Cinematic photorealistic 3D editorial render, {{ aspect | default('16:10') }} aspect ratio. Dramatic dusk / night-blue environment with rich depth-of-field, volumetric lighting, holographic floating glass panels with neon edge-glow (translucent rgba blue/cyan/amber/violet), shallow DoF bokeh, polished cinematic feel like a high-end product key-visual or VFX shot. NOT flat infographic, NOT vector illustration, NOT cartoon — photoreal 3D scene with composited holographic UI overlays.

GLOBAL SCENE LANGUAGE:
• Background: dark navy / space-blue gradient #0a0e1a → #1a2942, with subtle volumetric haze and bokeh particles. Hint of city skyline at dusk OR architectural interior OR sleek workspace floor with reflective surfaces.
• Floating UI panels: holographic glass with translucent rgba(15,20,30,0.55) fill, 1.5px neon edge stroke, soft drop-shadow glow, slight perspective tilt so they feel 3D in space. Inside each panel: clean type, icons, mini-charts.
• Numbered annotations: glowing circle badges (①②③) with thin radial lines connecting to the element they label. Color-coded by accent palette.
• Glowing connecting wires/beams between elements: thin neon lines (1–2px) with bloom, suggesting data flow.
• Color accents: {{ palette_accents | join(', ') }} — used as neon edge glow on panels, glyph tints, and connector beams. Keep palette tight (3–4 hues max) for cinematic cohesion.
• Footer line at bottom-center: "@tranvanhoang.com" — small uppercase letterspaced light-grey type, like a film credit.

ALL on-image text in VIETNAMESE WITH FULL DIACRITICS — only brand names ({{ brand_list | default('CLAUDE, ANTHROPIC') }}) and {{ tech_or_symbols | default('currency/math symbols ($, %, ×, ₫, →)') }} stay in English.

COMPOSITION STRUCTURE — {{ visual_type | default('three-pillar') }}:
{% if visual_type == 'before-after' %}
Two cinematic zones side-by-side. LEFT = old/pain side rendered in muted rose/amber neon. RIGHT = new/solution side in lime/cyan neon. Center: a glowing transition beam or arch connecting them with a delta label hovering mid-air.
{% elif visual_type == 'mind-map' %}
Central holographic orb (the topic) projecting 4–6 radial beams out to floating glass-panel nodes. Each node holds a 1–2 word label. Connectors glow in the accent palette.
{% elif visual_type == 'flowchart' %}
Horizontal chain of 3–5 floating glass panels connected by glowing arrow-beams. Optional decision diamond. Each panel labelled (≤3 words) with a small glyph icon.
{% elif visual_type == 'matrix-2x2' %}
2×2 grid of floating glass tiles in mid-air. Top-right quadrant glows strongest (winner) with lime/cyan halo. Two axis label-bars on left + bottom edges. Each tile holds a short label + glyph.
{% elif visual_type == 'venn' %}
Two or three luminous translucent spheres overlapping in mid-air. Each sphere has a floating label. Intersection zone glows brightest with shared-concept label.
{% elif visual_type == 'timeline' %}
Horizontal glowing axis stretching across the scene with 3–5 milestone markers (luminous orbs or glass cubes). Each milestone has a date-label panel and a 1-line description floating above.
{% elif visual_type == 'pyramid' %}
A translucent 3-tier pyramid hologram standing center-stage, each tier glowing with a distinct accent color and a glass-panel label hovering beside it. Camera angle slightly low, hero perspective.
{% elif visual_type == 'comparison-table' %}
A holographic comparison matrix panel in mid-air: rows = criteria, columns = options. ✓ / ✗ marks glow green/red. Header row in bold accent color.
{% elif visual_type == 'iceberg' %}
A holographic horizontal water-plane bisects the scene. ABOVE = a single glowing label (the visible symptom). BELOW (depth, mistier) = 3–5 hidden labels floating in the deep, fainter glow.
{% elif visual_type == 'cycle' %}
Circular ring of 3–5 floating glass nodes orbiting a central glow. Curved arrow-beams between them show direction of flow. Each node labelled with a glyph + 1–2 words.
{% elif visual_type == 'funnel' %}
A trapezoid funnel hologram narrowing top→bottom in mid-air. 3–5 tiers, each a translucent layer with a count-number and 1-line label. Glowing droplet at the bottom.
{% elif visual_type == 'concept-map' %}
5–8 floating glass nodes connected by labelled glowing edges. EVERY edge has a small relationship verb label (e.g. 'gây ra', 'cần', 'mở khóa').
{% elif visual_type == 'icon-grid' %}
Even grid (2×2, 3×3, or 2×3) of floating glass tiles, each tile = glowing glyph icon + 1-line label. Equal visual weight, slight 3D perspective tilt.
{% elif visual_type == 'number-infographic' %}
ONE giant glowing 3D number floating hero-center, with a holographic glyph icon beside it and a 1-line label below. The number dominates with strong bloom + lens-flare.
{% elif visual_type == 'three-pillar' %}
Three equal floating glass pillars (or panels) standing side-by-side in 3D space. Each pillar has a glyph at top, a tier-letter/short value mid, and a 1-line label below. Slight depth perspective.
{% elif visual_type == 'three-pillar-pyramid' %}
Same as pyramid — 3 stacked tiers with widest at bottom (majority) and narrowest at top (rare achievers).
{% else %}
Custom layout (see metaphor block below):
{{ layout_description }}
{% endif %}

