{% if subtitle_vi %}• Subtitle below in regular weight light-grey #B4BAC9: "{{ subtitle_vi }}".
{% endif %}• Annotation labels in clean sans (16–18px equivalent), white/light-cyan with neon edge glow on numbered badges. Mono-spaced numerals for stats.
• Footer "@tranvanhoang.com" in uppercase, 0.18em letterspacing, light grey #6A7080, bottom-center, film-credit feel.

