RENDER STYLE: cinematic 3D photoreal key-visual + holographic UI compositing. Inspired by Transform Group / Anthropic key visuals — dark cinematic environment, neon-edge glass panels, glowing connectors, numbered annotations, depth-of-field bokeh, volumetric haze. Palette: dark navy/space-blue base with accent neon glows in {{ palette_accents | join(', ') }}. Strong directional rim-lighting, subtle reflections on floor or surface. NOT flat infographic, NOT cartoon, NOT line-illustration — render as if it's a still from a high-end tech product launch film.

NEGATIVE: flat vector style, hand-drawn doodle, cream paper texture, parchment, vintage feel, line-illustration only, comic-book shading, low-poly, pixel art, overly saturated, cluttered text, English text outside brand names, missing Vietnamese diacritics, illegible labels, watermarks, copyright stamps, generic stock-photo people.
